 was being written, I was convinced that there was still plenty of time.\",\"\\\"A squat grey building of only thirty-four stories.\\\"\",\"A squat grey building of only thirty-four stories.\",\"A SQUAT grey building of only thirty-four stories.\"],\"key\":\"/works/OL64365W\",\"title\":\"Brave New World\"},{\"author_name\":[\"Aldous Huxley\"],\"cover_edition_key\":\"OL9236217M\",\"edition_key\":[\"OL58764524M\",\"OL40295210M\",\"OL50563313M\",\"OL48595364M\",\"OL39275068M\",\"OL52587970M\",\"OL28744268M\",\"OL23274400M\",\"OL9230441M\",\"OL32705922M\",\"OL15052604M\",\"OL19132839M\",\"OL22111634M\",\"OL5159493M\",\"OL3301586M\",\"OL9174573M\",\"OL7283881M\",\"OL16073491M\",\"OL9236217M\",\"OL7281510M\",\"OL19157094M\",\"OL5384180M\",\"OL2905400M\",\"OL22118450M\",\"OL9863728M\",\"OL9238588M\",\"OL21195432M\",\"OL13057435M\"],\"first_publish_year\":1942,\"first_sentence\":[\"Era un fuerte edificio de treinta y cuatro pisos.\",\"A squat grey building of only thirty-four stories.\",\"A SQUAT grey building of only thirty-four stories.\"],\"key\":\"/works/OL64440W\",\"title\":\"Brave New World and Brave New World Revisited\"},{\"author_name\":[\"Aldous Huxley\"],\"cover_edition_key\":\"OL24211093M\",\"edition_key\":[\"OL32221142M\",\"OL13649712M\",\"OL7318851M\",\"OL22615591M\",\"OL20743381M\",\"OL7275143M\",\"OL5515866M\",\"OL22788300M\",\"OL13649819M\",\"OL4596713M\",\"OL24211093M\",\"OL9873132M\",\"OL9237320M\",\"OL13820524M\",\"OL24211086M\",\"OL11316124M\",\"OL3557558M\",\"OL9229852M\",\"OL23757366M\",\"OL22601191M\",\"OL7282613M\",\"OL13816287M\",\"OL23377016M\",\"OL22820779M\",\"OL23249360M\",\"OL7282245M\",\"OL45655M\",\"OL5848457M\",\"OL9236952M\",\"OL9273506M\",\"OL9487913M\",\"OL13750278M\",\"OL19601686M\"],\"first_publish_year\":1962,\"first_sentence\":[\"\\\"ATTENTION,\\\" A VOICE BEGAN TO CALL, AND IT WAS AS THOUGH an oboe had suddenly become articulate.\",\"'Attention,' a voice began to call, and it was a though oboe had suddenly become articulate.\",\"\\\